Email address update
--------------------

Hi <%= @email %>,

<% if @resource.try(:unconfirmed_email?) %>
A request has been made to change the email address on your Mellow Menu account to <%= @resource.unconfirmed_email %>.

You'll receive a confirmation email at the new address before the change takes effect.
<% else %>
The email address on your Mellow Menu account has been successfully changed to <%= @resource.email %>.
<% end %>

If you did not make this change, please contact us immediately:
https://mellow.menu/#contact
